caption.p: Example photomicrographs of rat testis stained with hematoxylin and eosin (H&E ). The photomicrographs showed the magnification: × 10 (left) and × 20 (right) in each group . ( a) Normal control group. ( b) DM control group. ( c) DM+CCM 0.1 g/kg group. ( d) DM+CCM 0.5 g/kg group. ( e) DM+CCM 1 g/kg group. ( f) DM+Sildenafil 5 mg/kg group.
